				<a class='comment-reply-link' href='/2013/01/14/20191-taxons-lemploi-comme-pour-les-clopes-ca-motivera-les-taxes-a-arreter?replytocom=99211#respond' onclick='return addComment.moveForm("comment-99211", "99211", "respond", "20191")'>Répondre</a>							</div>
